de.axnsoftware.settings.impl.accessor

Class AbstractAccessorImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.axnsoftware.settings.impl.accessor.AbstractAccessorImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IAccessor, Cloneable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractPropertyAccessorImpl, RootAccessorImpl

    public abstract class AbstractAccessorImpl
extends Object
implements IAccessor
    The abstract class AbstractAccessorImpl models the root of a hierarchy of derived classes and it provides the default behaviour for all implementations of the IAccessor interface.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Carsten Klein "cklein"
